         <ab>VVrS27.1 (ms. 2005, 4000, 4010, 4020, 4025, 4030a, 4040, 4050, 4055, 4060, 4161, 4162):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">            
            taštag kē-š hōm ud urwarām andar ān-iz ī-š ǰīwām andar abāg abastāg abāz dārišn <em>ahurāi mazdāi haomą āuuaēδaiiamahī</em> ...</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "He has to hold up the saucer that contains <em>hōm</em> and <em>urwarām</em> and the one that contains the <em>ǰīwām</em> while reciting the <em>abastāg</em> 
            <em>ahurāi mazdāi haomą āuuaēδaiiamahī</em> ..."</ab>
